     H            Y.
     F** UTLR39 ****************************************************
     F*  PROGRAM: UTILITY- CHECK ENVIRONMENT TEST OR PRODUCTION?   *
     F*  WRITTEN: JW (SRA)  2020.02.07                             *
     F*------------------------------------------------------------*
     F*  CALLING SEQ.
     F*                    CALL 'UTLR39'
     F*                    PARM           $RTN    1
     F* ----------------------------
     F*   OUT $RTN  :  "T" TEST, "H" PRODUCTION
     F******************************************************
     FAB#EP00 IF  E           K        DISK         KINFDS INF1
     IINF1        DS
     I                                     *STATUS  @STTS
     I                                       83  92 #FILE
     I                                       93 102 #LIB
     I                                    B 156 1590#RCNT
     I                                        1 256 ARA
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           $RTN    1
      *--------------------------------------------------------
      *                    MAIN PROCESS
      *--------------------------------------------------------
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    LTR10  10
     C           LTR10     CHAINAB#EP00              99
     C           *IN99     IFEQ *OFF
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     MOVEL#LIB      $RTN
      *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
